<h1>Confirm Your Email Address</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.first_name || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for signing up for <%= @app_name %>! To complete your registration, please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>" class="button">Confirm Email Address</a>
</div>

<p>If the button above doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace;">
  <%= @confirmation_url %>
</p>

<p>This confirmation link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.</p>

<p>If you didn't create an account with us, please ignore this email.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The LocalServiceHub Team</p>